        <item>
            <title>拉斯维加斯世上最大球型场馆 MSG Sphere 落成，覆盖最高解像度巨型 LED 显示屏</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/msg-sphere/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=msg-sphere</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/msg-sphere/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 02:27:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSG Sphere]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[世上最大球型场馆]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[沉浸式体验]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198067</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>全新科技建筑 MSG Sphere 于 9 月 29 日在美国拉斯维加斯正式落成。身为世上最大球型场馆的 MSG Sphere 采用最先进的技术和设计，将音讯、视讯和感官效果融为一体，为观众创造了一种全新的沉浸式体验。整个 MSG Sphere 总斥资约 23 亿美元（约港币 180 亿元）建成。</p><p>MSG Sphere 的外围由分辨率达 16K x 16K 的巨型 LED 显示屏组成，是全球分辨率最高的 LED 屏幕。该屏幕可以向上、向下和围绕观众，营造出令人目眩神迷的视觉效果，让观众置身于一个完全沉浸式的环境中，仿佛身临其境。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.58.44.png"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198072" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.58.44-694x339.png" alt="" width="694" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.58.44-694x339.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.58.44-1280x626.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.58.44-768x375.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.58.44-1536x751.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.58.44.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.28.png"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198073" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.28-694x334.png" alt="" width="694" height="334" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.28-694x334.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.28-1280x616.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.28-768x370.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.28-1536x739.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.28.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.54.png"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198074" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.54-694x355.png" alt="" width="694" height="355" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.54-694x355.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.54-1280x655.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.54-768x393.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.54-1536x786.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-09-08.59.54.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>此外，MSG Sphere 采用了先进的音响技术，包括专为 MSG Sphere 开发的波束成形音响系统。 全新的音响系统能以精确的方式将声音引导到特定的区域，创造出更逼真的音讯效果。观众可以感受到音乐和声音从四面八方包围而来，增强了整体的观赏体验。</p><p>MSG Sphere 亦引入了多感官的 4D 制作元素，进一步提升了观众的参与感。配备次声波触觉系统的沉浸式座椅，能透过深层振动让观众身临其境地感受到雷声隆隆或摩托车轰鸣的震撼。MSG Sphere 也利用环境特效，如温度变化、凉风和特定气味，营造出更逼真的体验。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_25043"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GUsY8ocXVuk?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片来源：影片截图<br />
资料来源：<a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/culture/music/msg-sphere-las-vegas-cost-b1111086.html">Evening Standard</a>、<a href="https://liveforlivemusic.com/news/msg-sphere-reveals-first-sphere-experience-postcard-from-earth/">Live For Live Music</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
