            <title>加州就业部门文件揭露   Qualcomm 将裁减 1,200 名员工</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/qualcomm-laid-off-more-than-1200-staffs/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=qualcomm-laid-off-more-than-1200-staffs</link>
